#eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu is following this story. Courtesy #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Two people have been arrested in connection with the deadly Pietermaritzburg tavern shooting. Four people were killed over the weekend and more were hospitalised. READ: Four dead, eight wounded in Pietermaritzburg tavern shooting It is alleged two men driving a VW Polo stormed the tavern around 8:30pm and opened fire on patrons. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has more details in the video above.  